Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.94,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,658)}しの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「秋色」「閨情」
