Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.52,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,658)}かさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「情凝」「流光」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.57,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「千早」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.98,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,658)}もろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.98,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,658)}もも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「冷山」「九重」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.73,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,658)}ひさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.73,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,658)}きり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「晴春」「促織」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.15,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,658)}うか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.15,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(760,658)}うら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有「初瀨」「恨更」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在腦子裏是用第一個字來搶這些的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也應該感覺的到吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多…多多少少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是多少有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的能聽出來嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我的資料啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實 也不是只有你和周防名人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人說「感覺好」的人們 都有不少這樣的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是能提前分辨出下一個音的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要這些啦 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我過幾天會拿更像樣的東西報答你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是綾瀨同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行…好像在小聲地念咒一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 從這邊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千… 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.20,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,しらつゆに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「秋色潤原野」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.58,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,しのぶれど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「閨情芳心宿」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.00,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,ゆらのとを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「川急由良口」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.41,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,ゆふされば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「暮色沉田野」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.13,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,かくとだに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「情凝意暗結」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.59,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,かささぎの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「流光動銀漢」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「你好像也有20張」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.63,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬萊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牌的數目並不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「相信我吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是書桌小子幫我發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴了我「你能聽到」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我很羡慕」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.28,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,うかりける
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「初瀨謁觀音」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.20,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,うらみわび
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「恨更淚成雨」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.20,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,きりぎりす
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「促織絮寒夜」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.20,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,もろともに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「冷山絕人跡」
